title: Looking for Ranked Teammates!
body:
Hey Fellas,
My Summoner name is; Im Cancer.

My main account last season that I'd been playing on for 2ish years was Gold 4 then I get permabanned.
I'm now in Silver, S5 atm, just been going back and fourth through the ranks of Silver, over playing with the people I have on my friends list because they're toxic AF, funny but they run it down mid.

I was a Top main last season, towards the end changed to Jungle, now I mainly play either Jungle or Braum Support, yes, just Braum(occasionally Alistar) but yeah.
Looking for really anyone that'd be interested in playing, mainly Ranked, but I'm down for Norms, so fourth.

Cheers fellas, Have a good one!
